	<p>Following is the procedure to configure Chat Server:</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Stop&nbsp;<code>EF_ChatServer</code>&nbsp; service in Windows Services pane</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Navigate to&nbsp;<code>&lt;installation-dir&gt;\hybrid-chat\core\chat_server\config</code>&nbsp; directory</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Open&nbsp;<code>config.json</code>&nbsp;file with any text editor</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Save the file after configuration changes and start&nbsp;<code>EF_ChatServer</code>&nbsp; service</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Chat Server logs can be found at&nbsp;<code>/EFLogs/chat-solution/chat-server</code>&nbsp;</p>
 </li>
</ol>
